cs.SE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

The paper discusses the software engineering practice in the development of deep learning applications, which involves the use of machine learning algorithms (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) to analyze and process data, particularly in computer vision (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE). However, the focus of the paper is on the software engineering aspect, which includes the development life cycle of DL applications, making cs.SE the most likely sub-category.
